---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Read the Baila Canarias Dance Academy privacy policy to learn how we collect, use and protect your personal data."
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy policy</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bio-content">
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-light);font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:2rem;font-style:italic;">
          Last updated: June 2023
        </p>

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          Baila Canarias is a Latin dance school based in Tenerife, Canary Islands, Spain.
          Our website address is: https://www.bailacanarias.com.
        </p>

        <h2>What data we collect</h2>
        <p>
          When you subscribe to our mailing list, we collect your name, email address, dance
          role preference, and the dance styles you are interested in. This data is processed
          by MailChimp (Intuit Inc.) on our behalf.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use your data</h2>
        <p>
          We use your email address to send you updates about classes, events, workshops and
          other news from Baila Canarias. We will never sell or share your data with third
          parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You can unsubscribe from our mailing list at any time by clicking the unsubscribe
          link at the bottom of any email we send. You may also contact us at
          <a href="mailto:contact@bailacanarias.com">contact@bailacanarias.com</a> to request
          deletion of your data.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses no tracking cookies. We do not use Google Analytics or any
          third-party analytics service. MailChimp may set cookies when you interact with
          the signup form.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any privacy-related questions, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:contact@bailacanarias.com">contact@bailacanarias.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
